Git repository: https://github.com/mstratman/cpan-syntax

cpan-syntax is a collection of files and snippets to add syntax
highlighting to search.cpan.org

Dependencies:
* jQuery: http://jquery.com/
* mstratman's fork of jquery.styleswitch.mlklc.js:
  https://github.com/mstratman/FRAMEWORK/blob/master/jquery.plugins/jquery.styleswitch.mlklc.js
* jquery.cookie.js: https://github.com/carhartl/jquery-cookie
